Azure Bastion:
       Azure Bastion is a service you deploy that lets you connect to a virtual machine using your 
  browser and the Azure portal, or via the native SSH or RDP client already installed on your local computer
Prerequisite
    1 NSG
    1 Azure Bastion Host 
    N, VMs

connections will be
      user> azure portal>Vnet> Subnet> NSG> AzureBastion Host>-------------Target subnet2> no. of VMs 
